data.description: Country paradise with a serene and picturesque setting on ~1.5 acres! Perfect for your mini-farm homestead. Seller is offering VA assumable with an interest rate of 2.99%. This beautiful farmhouse has updates in all the right places to include a gas stove, ceiling-high cabinets, brick fireplace (gas) with solid wood mantle, shiplap, laminate flooring, barn door, huge walk-in shower, and much more! 2 bedrooms on each floor and a loft area upstairs! Covered deck with sounds of the creek in private backyard. Enjoy fishing from the creek or taking in the stunning views. Less than 10 miles to Ft. Campbell or Clarksville!
